Completion delight patterns for high-stakes learning products
Reducing cognitive load in exam-prep contexts
Toast/notification hygiene and when to remove UI elements vs. rewrite them

5. AI/ML product management

Feature scoping for ML-powered experiences (recommendations, nudges, predictions)
